# Reference List

Track professional references with the context recruiters need. Surface during late-stage offer conversations.

## Reference 1, <Name>

- **Title at time of working with you**: <e.g., "Senior Director of Engineering">
- **Current title and company**: <e.g., "VP Engineering at Acme">
- **Relationship**: <e.g., "Direct manager from 2020 to 2023">
- **Preferred contact**: <email or phone, and best time>
- **Approved talking points**: What this reference can speak to confidently.
  - <Point 1>
  - <Point 2>
- **Approved STAR stories**: What stories they remember and would speak to.
  - <Story 1>
- **Notes**: Anything special to flag (e.g., "knows me in a delivery context, not pre-sales").
- **Last contacted**: <YYYY-MM-DD>, status of their willingness to be contacted.

